## 3. Stage-by-Stage File & Storage Specifications

| Stage | Input Location (Check Order) | Primary Output Location | Cloud Delivery / Backup Destination |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **1. Image Generation** | Prompts from Job state | Local VM: `output/<date>/<theme_slug>/raw_data/` | GCS backup: `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/raw_data/` (Optional / Async) |
| **2. BG Removal** | 1. VM: `raw_data/`<br>2. GCS: `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/raw_data/`<br>3. Drive: `Clipart/raw_data/<date>/<theme_slug>/` | Local VM: `output/<date>/<theme_slug>/no_bg/` | **GCS Primary:** `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/no_bg/` |
| **3. Upscaling** | 1. VM: `no_bg/`<br>2. GCS: `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/no_bg/`<br>3. Drive: `Clipart/no_bg/<date>/<theme_slug>/` | Local VM: `output/<date>/<theme_slug>/upscaled/` | **Google Drive Primary:** `Clipart/main_data/<date>/<theme_slug>/`<br>**GCS Backup:** `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/upscaled/` |
| **4. Mockups & PDF** | 1. VM: `no_bg/` or `upscaled/`<br>2. GCS: `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/no_bg/`<br>3. Drive: `Clipart/main_data/<date>/<theme_slug>/` | Local VM: `output/<date>/<theme_slug>/mockups/` | **GCS Primary:** `Clipart/<date>/<theme_slug>/mockups/` & `pdf/`<br>**Google Drive:** `Clipart/raw_data/<date>/<theme_slug>/pdf/` |
| **5. Metadata & CSV** | 1. VM: `mockups/`<br>2. GCS: `mockups/` | Local VM: `output/<date>/all_listings.csv` | **GCS & Google Drive Dual Sync:** `csv/<date>/all_listings.csv` & `Clipart/csv/<date>/` |

