- Test single-VM execution (`python -m etsy_pipeline.pipeline.orchestrator`): Verify raw images stay local and no unnecessary download calls are triggered.
- Test multi-VM daemon execution (`run_bg_removal_worker.py --daemon` on a clean directory): Verify missing local files are retrieved from GCS/Drive seamlessly.
